trans-unit.source: Contains attributes of an associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
Not inheritable.
Gets a <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"></xref> that bounds the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"></xref> that bounds the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
Gets the horizontal resolution, in dots per inch, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
The horizontal resolution, in dots per inch, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
Gets the vertical resolution, in dots per inch, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
The vertical resolution, in dots per inch, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
Gets the size, in bytes, of the enhanced metafile plus header file.
The size, in bytes, of the enhanced metafile plus header file.
Returns a value that indicates whether the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is device dependent.
`true` if the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is device dependent; otherwise, `false`.
Returns a value that indicates whether the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows enhanced metafile format.
`true` if the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows enhanced metafile format; otherwise, `false`.
Returns a value that indicates whether the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows enhanced metafile format or the Windows enhanced metafile plus format.
`true` if the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows enhanced metafile format or the Windows enhanced metafile plus format; otherwise, `false`.
Returns a value that indicates whether the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows enhanced metafile plus format.
`true` if the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows enhanced metafile plus format; otherwise, `false`.
Returns a value that indicates whether the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Dual enhanced metafile format.
This format supports both the enhanced and the enhanced plus format.
`true` if the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Dual enhanced metafile format; otherwise, `false`.
Returns a value that indicates whether the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> supports only the Windows enhanced metafile plus format.
`true` if the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> supports only the Windows enhanced metafile plus format; otherwise, `false`.
Returns a value that indicates whether the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows metafile format.
`true` if the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows metafile format; otherwise, `false`.
Returns a value that indicates whether the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows placeable metafile format.
`true` if the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref> is in the Windows placeable metafile format; otherwise, `false`.
Gets the logical horizontal resolution, in dots per inch, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
The logical horizontal resolution, in dots per inch, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
Gets the logical vertical resolution, in dots per inch, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
The logical vertical resolution, in dots per inch, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
Gets the size, in bytes, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
The size, in bytes, of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
Gets the type of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.MetafileType"></xref> enumeration that represents the type of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
Gets the version number of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
The version number of the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
Gets the Windows metafile (WMF) header file for the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
A <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.MetaHeader"></xref> that contains the WMF header file for the associated <xref href="System.Drawing.Imaging.Metafile"></xref>.
